---
title: Pan-Seared Thyme Chicken with Buttery Carrots and Peas
description: Eating wholesome meals doesn't have to be boring. Tonight's elegant chicken dinner is elevated with a creamy pan sauce, roasted potatoes and a buttery finish of carrots and peas. Bon appetit!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-au-thym-poele-4ab87542.jpg
